                footerDesc: "Your personal AI-powered movie assistant. Discover your next favorite movie.",
                
                termsTitle: "Terms of Service",
                termsContent: "<h4>1. Nature of Service</h4><p class='mb-4'>CineMatch AI is an AI-powered movie recommendation platform. We do not host, stream, or distribute full movies.</p><h4>2. AI Disclaimer</h4><p class='mb-4'>Recommendations are generated by external algorithms (Google Gemini). We are not responsible for inaccurate, offensive, or incorrect responses generated by the AI.</p><h4>3. Age Restriction</h4><p class='mb-4'>The platform is intended for users aged 16 or older. AI recommendations may include R-rated or mature content.</p><h4>4. Platform Usage & Termination</h4><p class='mb-4'>You agree to use the platform lawfully. We reserve the right to terminate or suspend accounts at any time, without prior notice, for abuse or security reasons.</p><h4>5. Limitation of Liability</h4><p>The service is provided \"as is\". We do not guarantee 100% uptime, nor do we accept liability for any data loss, service interruptions, or errors.</p>",
                
                privacyTitle: "Privacy Policy",
                privacyContent: "<h4>1. Data Collection</h4><p class='mb-4'>We only collect essential information for your account (Username/Email and encrypted password). We do not track your browsing outside our platform.</p><h4>2. Data Security</h4><p class='mb-4'>Your passwords are securely encrypted using Bcrypt. We cannot access your real password.</p><h4>3. Data Sharing</h4><p class='mb-4'>CineMatch AI <b>does not sell</b> your data to third parties, marketing firms, or advertisers.</p><h4>4. Account Deletion</h4><p>You can request full deletion of your data and history by contacting our support.</p>",
                
                dmcaTitle: "Copyright Notice (DMCA)",
                dmcaContent: "<h4>Copyright and Intellectual Property Protection</h4><p class='mb-4'>CineMatch AI is <b>strictly a recommendation and cataloging service</b>. Our servers <b>do not host, upload, or transmit</b> video files, movies, TV shows, or any copyrighted media.</p><h4>Data Source</h4><p class='mb-4'>Images (posters), synopses, and metadata displayed on this platform are fetched via public databases and third-party APIs (such as TMDB - The Movie Database). These contents remain the intellectual property of their respective studios and production companies. CineMatch AI displays them under <i>Fair Use</i> strictly for informational and recommendation purposes.</p><h4>Content Removal (DMCA)</h4><p>If you are the copyright holder of any content displayed incorrectly and wish to have it removed from our visual catalog, please email info@cinematchai.com and we will remove the references immediately.</p>",
                
                faqTitle: "Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)",
                faqContent: "<details class='mb-2 bg-slate-800 rounded p-3 cursor-pointer group'><summary class='font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-sky-400'>Is CineMatch AI free?</summary><p class='mt-2 text-slate-400 text-sm'>Yes! Basic platform usage is 100% free. We rely on donations to keep our servers running.</p></details><details class='mb-2 bg-slate-800 rounded p-3 cursor-pointer group'><summary class='font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-sky-400'>Can I watch movies here?</summary><p class='mt-2 text-slate-400 text-sm'>No. CineMatch AI is an engine to discover new movies. We are not a streaming platform.</p></details><details class='mb-2 bg-slate-800 rounded p-3 cursor-pointer group'><summary class='font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-sky-400'>How does the AI work?</summary><p class='mt-2 text-slate-400 text-sm'>We use Google Gemini. Our system analyzes your prompt and history to instruct the AI to find the perfect movies for your taste.</p></details>",
                
                cookieText: "CineMatch AI uses local storage to save your preferences and keep your session active. By continuing to use the site, you agree to our Privacy Policy.",
                cookieBtn: "I Understand"
            },
